    	<div class="accordion-item mb-3">
    		<h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingCancellation">
    			<button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseCancellation" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseCancellation">
    				What is NECYSC's cancellation policy for submitted registrations?
    			</button>
    		</h2>
    		<div id="collapseCancellation" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingCancellation" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
    			<div class="accordion-body">
    				<strong>Cancellation/Refunds Policy:</strong><br />
					Camp fee is non-transferable. Refunds of any portion of the camp fee (minus $250 processing fee) may only be made when written notice of cancellation and a request for refund (email: <a href="mailto:director@necysc.org">director@necysc.org</a>) is received by May 15th, 2026. There is no refunds after End of Day May 15th, 2026.<br /><br />
					<strong>Cancellations Due to Medical or Emergency Circances</strong><br />
					In some cases, refunds may be granted after the cancellation and refund period for medical or emergency circumstances only. A written notice of cancellation with explanation of medical or emergency circumstances must be provided (email: <a href="mailto:director@necysc.org">director@necysc.org</a>) for a refund request to be considered. Additional documentation may be requested by the NECYSC. Partial refunds for medical or emergency circumstances will be at the discretion of NECYSC after reviewing the request.
    			</div>
    		</div>
    	</div>
